item.title: Learn Everything Entrepreneurs and Freelancers Need to Know About Accounting
item.description:
Learn Everything Entrepreneurs and Freelancers Need to Know About Accounting

Avoid tax penalties, limit your liability, and keep more of your money Tired of reading through 30 different browser tabs looking for answers to your basic accounting questions? "Surely someone has already answered this" you tell yourself. It's not like you're the first person to ever have to report expenses or run payroll.
